title: Turbo Pyro - 10 Fireworks Projects You Can Make This Weekend
description:
Turbo Pyro - 10 Fireworks Projects You Can Make This Weekend
By Ned Gorski

206 pages, extensive photographs and links for 70+ videos detail how to make the following projects:

Flying Fish Mines
Pumped Star Mines
Tube Sparklers
Fountains
Wheels
Magnum Bottle Rockets
Helicopter
Stinger Missiles (spin-stabilized rocket)
Hummers & Whirlwinds
Aerial Shells
